            "id": "data-engineering",
            "title": "Data Engineering",
            "description": "Infrastructure that moves, transforms, and stores data at scale.",
            "longDescription": "Data engineering is the foundation of every modern data platform. It covers how raw data is ingested, modeled, orchestrated, and delivered reliably to downstream analytics, science, and product teams.",
